-wearables&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id= &quot;geO0A2&quot;>;新款可穿戴设备面向广泛的受众，从休闲用户到户外运动员。三星 Galaxy Ring 是一款时尚的可穿戴设备，更像是一款谨慎的健康追踪器，而 Galaxy Watch 7 是一款智能手表，更具有新的睡眠呼吸暂停检测功能。但它的功能并不像三星 Galaxy Watch Ultra 那样丰富，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung -galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:23:37-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:23:37-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy 拆封：2024 年 7 月活动中宣布的所有内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色、蓝色和水绿色背景上的三星徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/j30lXEiclgq_A3r3_h4CIMAulZo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452722/acastro_STK075_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;三星推出了 Galaxy Ring、Galaxy Watch Ultra、新款 Z Fold 和 Z Flip 手机等。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>宋茜</name><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name><name>理查德·劳勒</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>最高法院 NetChoice 裁决的后果</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;最高法院大楼的照片插图，带有像素化的红白条纹。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-_j8bu4miMeay7jIXHchVU4QLYw=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452898/STK463_SCOTUS_D.0.jpg&quot;/ >; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制 |照片来自 Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;以下是 SCOTUS 的决定对从儿童在线安全法到 TikTok“禁令”等各个方面可能意味着的含义。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>索尼新款 ZV-E10 II 相机旨在让视频博主远离 1,000 美元的手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;白色的索尼 ZV-E10 II，坐在桌子上，镜头已拆卸。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RzXhtCLNqP3vNHyi2owvJdAN2vk=/0x0:7726x5151/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452911/BFARSACE_ZVE10II_1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;ZV-E10 II 看起来非常像其 2021 年的前身。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7Gv7iG&quot;>;涓滴经济可能很垃圾，但索尼对于相机中的技术，仍然是坚定的信徒。新款 ZV-E10 II 延续了索尼的趋势，即从昂贵的相机到更实惠的型号进行小规模的迭代改变。只是它永远不会没有一些权衡。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;4LKvq5&quot;>;ZV-E10 II 是 APS-C 无反光镜系统相机的后续产品 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/22702421/sony-alpha-zv-e10-review-vlogging-camera-test-price-specs&quot;>;2021 年的 ZV-E10&lt;/a>;，现在配备更大的电池、26 兆像素背照式传感器，并改进了 4K 视频。 8 月初推出时，机身售价为 999 美元，与索尼新款 PZ 16-50mm f/3.5-5.6 OSS II 镜头捆绑售价为 1,099 美元，与 &lt;a href=&quot; 等旗舰手机的价格相当。 https://www.theverge.com/23899983/iphone-15-pro-max-camera-apple-full-frame&quot;>;iPhone 15 Pro Max&lt;/a>;。但是，当然，即使是最好的 iPhone 相机也有...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii -vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 有较小的更新和更高的价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三星 Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 智能手机的上手照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/I66riB7OyE8CUtS7R-uBM9xNMu4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452748/DSCF8089.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;炎热的可折叠夏天正如火如荼地进行，你们大家。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;opCbaW&quot;>;如果您还有任何剩余的希望，尽管&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/ 3/24191966/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-spec-leak&quot;>;泄漏&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188017/ samsung-galaxy-z-flip-fold-6-leak-renders-colors-unpacked&quot;>;泄漏&lt;/a>;，三星的可折叠手机今年将进行重大更新，那么我不想成为坏消息的传播者。它们更耐用一点，更轻一点，并且有一些微小的升级。即便如此，这两款机型都获得了某种程度的提升：价格上涨，Galaxy Z Fold 6 现在的起价为 1,899 美元，Z Flip 6 的起价为 1,099 美元。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;WjhfvK&quot;>;两款手机均采用专门为三星调校的 Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 芯片组，与 S24 系列一样，它们都包含七年的操作系统和安全更新支持。由于铰链设计和材料的改进，它们都更加坚固，并声称具有更好的抗跌落能力。内部柔性玻璃也更耐用，而且...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z- Fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy Watch Ultra 上手体验：超级似曾相识</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Galaxy Watch Ultra 视图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lVAlvegcCx6horuGR3JrU5QVcC4=/0x0:4032x2688/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/73452769/galaxywatchultra4.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;肯定是松鼠画。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;这是 Apple Watch Ultra，但适用于 Android。哦，Galaxy Watch 7 也在这里。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-功能价格&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-features-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-features-price</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>三星新款 Galaxy Buds 在形式和功能上都是公然的 AirPod 克隆</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三星 Galaxy Buds 3 / Galaxy Buds 3 Pro 的实际产品照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/26UyHrvmjER1lhrtKzJzqbOWzsE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452746/DSCF8067_Enhanced_NR.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UZHf7M&quot;>;除了最新的折叠手机和可穿戴设备外，三星还推出了新款 Galaxy Buds 3 Pro 和 Galaxy Buds 3。 com/2024/7/5/24192554/someone-already-bought-samsungs-galaxy-buds3-pro&quot;>;和早期销售&lt;/a>;）证实，该公司已经放弃了过去几代的微妙入耳式设计茎状外观赋予它们类似 AirPods 的外观和感觉——尤其是白色。两款耳塞均采用青铜灰色饰面，与棱角分明的“刀片”设计相结合，让我想起了特斯拉的 Cyber​​truck。但不可否认的是，它与苹果广受欢迎的 AirPods 总体上有相似之处。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;D8k3an&quot;>;三星的新闻稿称，这一转变是“收集到的各种统计数据”的直接结果，这些数据表明柄形因素可产生更好的舒适度和入耳稳定性。所以，我们在这里......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy Ring 可能是统治生态系统的唯一戒指</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在其外壳中持有 Galaxy Ring 的人&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/YcBPYKFtyCgjtA6ayg_yQa0HEwg=/0x0:8064x5376/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73452758/galaxyring5.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;售价 399.99 美元，无需订阅，从 7 月 24 日开始正式发售。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;硬件很坚固。这些想法很有趣。只要在测试中表现出色，三星就可能获胜。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24194938/samsung-galaxy-ring-hands-on-price -unpacked-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24194938/samsung-galaxy-ring-hands-on-price-unpacked-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24194938/samsung-galaxy-ring-hands-on-price-unpacked-2024</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T08:20:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T08:20:00-04:00</updated><title>智能家居如何搬家</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;起重机将大脑移出智能家居的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RpIoVtoh6HQXRpRzLi93guAMPlY=/1x0:3481x2320/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452698/247132_SMART_HOME_MOVE_JGibbs.0.jpg ” />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Jackson Gibbs for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;搬出和搬进智能家居需要非常注重细节。本指南将帮助您完成它。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24184716/moving-smart-home-tech-setup&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24184716/moving-smart-home-tech-setup" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24184716/moving-smart-home-tech-setup</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T08:00:13-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T08:00:13-04:00</updated><title>塑料垃圾箱：比盒子更好</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;插图：两名专业搬运工搬运装在即将散架的纸板箱中的物品。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sQMeGeuHX7pBJln9y_rWxvkvzi4=/0x1：4054x2704/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452675/247132_CARDBOARD_BOXES_JGibbs.0。 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Jackson Gibbs for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;租用垃圾箱很方便，更可持续，而且我一次也没有错过纸板箱。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/24176469/moving-boxes- Plastic-bins-cardboard&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24176469/moving-boxes-plastic-bins-cardboard" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24176469/moving-boxes- Plastic-bins-cardboard</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry></feed>